ISLAMABAD, Nov 03 (APP):Jamiat Ulema Islam-Fazl (JUI-F) Chief Maulana Faz-ur-Rehman on Thursday condemned the tragic incident of firing on the rally of Pakistan Tehreek-e-Insaf in Wazirabad.
Maulana Fazl who is also the head of Pakistan Democratic Movement said this incident had left a big question mark on the performance of Punjab government related to the law and order situation in the province.He also prayed for early recovery of the injured.
